    excerpt: 'Discover overlooked poison hazards for toddlers beyond common cleaners. Learn practical tips to secure medicines, cosmetics, plants & more, keeping your child safe.',
    metaDescription: 'Discover overlooked poison hazards for toddlers beyond common cleaners. Learn practical tips to secure medicines, cosmetics, plants & more, keeping your child safe.',
    readTime: 6,
    date: 'April 2026',
