    slug: 'hidden-poison-risks-toddlers-every-room-home',
    title: 'Beyond the Cabinet: Uncovering Hidden Poison Risks for Toddlers in Every Room of Your Home',
    category: 'Child Safety',
    excerpt: 'Discover overlooked poison dangers for toddlers in your home, from bedrooms to bathrooms. Learn to identify and secure unexpected toxic items in every room.',
    metaDescription: 'Discover overlooked poison dangers for toddlers in your home, from bedrooms to bathrooms. Learn to identify and secure unexpected toxic items in every room.',
