    category: 'Child Safety',
    excerpt: 'Ensure peace of mind before baby arrives with our comprehensive pre-baby nursery safety audit checklist. Essential tips for first-time parents to prevent accidents.',
    metaDescription: 'Ensure peace of mind before baby arrives with our comprehensive pre-baby nursery safety audit checklist. Essential tips for first-time parents to prevent accidents.',
    readTime: 6,
